Install Eclipse and JDK: 
https://www.ntu.edu.sg/home/ehchua/programming/howto/EclipseJava_HowTo.html

JDK installation:
https://www.ntu.edu.sg/home/ehchua/programming/howto/JDK_HowTo.html#jdk-install

Eclipse Debug to gdb debug cmds mapping:
F5  ->  s (step)
f6  ->  n (next)
f7  ->  fin (finish)
f8  ->  c (continue)

To understand all the zookeeper config:  server/quorum/QuorumPeerConfig.java
              put break at function: public void parseProperties(Properties zkProp)
